🔥 4. Best Practice (rất quan trọng)

Bạn nên viết 1 function tổng hợp:

Public Sub EnsureAddIn(addinName As String, Optional addinPath As String = "")

    Dim ai As AddIn
    Dim found As Boolean
    found = False

    ' Tìm trong danh sách
    For Each ai In Application.AddIns
        If LCase(ai.Name) = LCase(addinName) Then
            ai.Installed = True
            found = True
            Exit For
        End If
    Next ai

    ' Nếu chưa có → add từ path
    If found = False And addinPath <> "" Then
        Set ai = Application.AddIns.Add(addinPath, True)
        ai.Installed = True
    End If

End Sub

👉 Gọi từ UiPath:

{"MyAddin.xlam", "C:\Addins\MyAddin.xlam"}


